content:
Hehehe~heh! What is this, some kind of mind-reading magic?
Just got exactly the gift I wanted,
Could it be... are you the Chrysovian Astralink?!{什么？}

I plan to put it in the biggest fish tank there is—the ocean! {短暂停}
Just kidding.
I really like it and will take good care of it. Thank you!

...Oh, it's alive.
Thanks, I'll take good care of it...{短暂停}
Barring any special circumstances, it should survive at my place.

Hmm...{短暂停}
I think I misunderstood something,
Maybe today isn't the best day to receive gifts.

Fish? {短暂停}
I wonder how it'll taste...
Thanks anyway!

A gift? If it's from you, {短暂停}
Even if it's something mischievous, I'll gladly accept it.
I'll take care of it.

What if I told you... I dreamed you gave me a present...
Would you laugh at me? {微笑}
Eh? You actually have a present for me?!

Let me open it and see, it's a <color=#8AAB4B>{礼物}</color>, {短暂停}
You really scared me there,
Interesting.

I have a guess that I'm a bit shy to say...
Um...{短暂停}
Were you just{短暂停}picking out a gift for me?

I'll let you in on a secret, {短暂停}
Actually, I have a surprise for you too!
This <color=#8AAB4B>{回礼}</color>!

Hmm...{短暂停}
I think I misunderstood something,
Maybe today isn't the best day to receive gifts.

It's fine, yeah. {微笑}
Just my hopes and dreams being crushed, that's all.
I don't mind at all, really. {微笑}

Did you bring this gift specially for me?
Thank you! Each day brings a delightful surprise,
from both friends and life itself.{开心}

Though it might be a bit rude to expect presents from someone you just met{短暂停}
Like, just a lickle bit impolite,
But you just can't hide how excited you are about it!

This... is, {短暂停}
delightful.
<color=#d3b037>{me}</color>, thank you.
